message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and expectations. Given its value and the benefits it offers, I believe we can come to an agreement that satisfies both of us. Considering its worth to you, I propose a price of $9,500 for the product. This price reflects its high quality and the significant return on investment you can expect. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to discuss this further.
